headline: Paychex, Inc. Schedules Fourth Quarter Fiscal 2025 Earnings Conference Call for June 25, 2025
summary: ROCHESTER, N.Y., June 13, 2025--Paychex, Inc. (Nasdaq: PAYX) will release financial results for its fiscal 2025 fourth quarter ended May 31, 2025 before the financial markets open on Wednesday, June 25, 2025.
